{"tid":1978931,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Eason 直播隱藏黃藍是政見，黑白是良知","createTime":"2020-04-19T05:22:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-19T07:55:29.000Z","uid":41658,"like":1,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e7097131a17b9fac13ee4428f5e303b4fdfe1318","tid":1978931,"uid":41658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T05:22:54.000Z","msg":"雖然著藍色杉，但周圍黃色，仲有鋼琴隱喻黑白，唔反la<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ace4438ffcbbfbec0ac79f86a463caeed96600f","tid":1978931,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T05:24:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />【黃色經濟圈】當<del>黃子華</del> 陳奕迅 都不夠黃<br />\n<br />\n純黃經濟圈，很難行得通。「光時」同樣面對挑戰，物流、選貨，全部對紅色資本說不，現實中是個制肘。<br />\n<br />\n市場是現實，如果有深黃店開在長洲深處，市區人都不會日日坐船懲罰。何況，到全世界都轉黃，黃店就只是輿論力量和自由，市場還是會自然調節。<br />\n<br />\n有人批評，<del>子華</del> 單丸 在反送中以來沒有發言。<br />\n<br />\n當我們對陳巧文萬分愧疚，不會有追問「六月以來佢做過咩」。因為，網民覺得陳巧文是犧牲者，而黃子華，是反共的「得益者」。"},{"pid":"30fe2e75f6e4e478e76bcc034d01be7ceb66a419","tid":1978931,"uid":93986,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T05:26:18.000Z","msg":"支那旗粒星都係黃色，黃到金"},{"pid":"d10ca9d2c7691a287f2ce37096af443243be4f49","tid":1978931,"uid":235152,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T06:14:01.000Z","msg":"算啦人地無認又用實際行動證明係藍<br />\n咪入綠色觀察名單<br />\n非黑即白只會殺死長頭草埋藍堆<br />\n多一個朋友好過多一個敵人"},{"pid":"7f7ad73a54bf2390489fb2a54fb7df8fa67d9534","tid":1978931,"uid":239525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T07:47:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"273338888ce5aba9ae54b6004515bbd84c74df4b","tid":1978931,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7f7ad73a54bf2390489fb2a54fb7df8fa67d9534","tid":1978931,"uid":239525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T07:47:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T07:55:29.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}